OL,5, Rail firm Avanti West Coast has been   
OL,6, warned it needs to "drastically improve
OL,7, services" after its contract to run the
OL,8, London to Glasgow line was extended by 
OL,9, just six months.                       
OL,11,FThe decision means it will continue to 
OL,12,Frun services until next April, the     
OL,13,FDepartment for Transport said.         
OL,15,FAvanti has come under fire after       
OL,16,Fslashing its timetables in August.     
OL,17,FTrains between London and Manchester   
OL,18,Fwere the worst affected.               
OL,20,FIt had apologised for the problems.    
